ntent":"即便知道从开始便已注定","from":129.24,"location":2,"to":133.68},{"content":"唯有今天 就在我的脚下","from":133.68,"location":2,"to":140.5},{"content":"以你的本来面目 闪烁光亮","from":140.81,"location":2,"to":145.13},{"content":"真可爱啊","from":154.0,"location":2,"to":156.12},{"content":"走得真好","from":161.36,"location":2,"to":162.91},{"content":"真乖","from":163.57,"location":2,"to":165.37},{"content":"德子","from":166.44,"location":2,"to":167.21},{"content":"知盛兄长","from":167.84,"location":2,"to":169.16},{"content":"呀 小皇子已经能站起来了啊","from":169.16,"location":2,"to":172.06},{"content":"这位似乎是重盛兄长的侍童…","from":172.23,"location":2,"to":175.45},{"content":"这是琵琶","from":175.93,"location":2,"to":176.69},{"content":"他的一只眼睛 怎会和兄长的一样？","from":179.85,"location":2,"to":182.05},{"content":"难不成是重盛兄长的私生子？","from":182.27,"location":2,"to":184.83},{"content":"不是的","from":185.24,"location":2,"to":186.38},{"content":"抱歉 还以为定是如此","from":188.24,"location":2,"to":190.26},{"content":"你看 陛下他也新添了皇子…","from":190.26,"location":2,"to":192.83},{"content":"我又说错话了","from":199.52,"location":2,"to":202.07},{"content":"这孩子有弟弟了 却是另一个母亲生的","from":204.57,"location":2,"to":208.22},{"content":"是小督？","from":208.81,"location":2,"to":209.9},{"content":"是另一位 叫殖子夫人","from":210.13,"location":2,"to":213.53},{"content":"听说 兄长您的夫人在当那孩子的乳母？","from":218.18,"location":2,"to":222.22},{"content":"嗯 是的","from":223.29,"location":2,"to":224.9},{"content":"还听说您已经受命担任宗盛兄长的辅佐","from":226.0,"location":2,"to":229.27},{"content":"嗯 和弟弟重衡一起","from":229.55,"location":2,"to":232.66},{"content":"不知宗盛兄长能否胜任家主之位","from":233.13,"location":2,"to":235.67},{"content":"嗯 这个…","from":236.37,"location":2,"to":237.94},{"content":"父亲怎样了？","from":239.07,"location":2,"to":239.94},{"content":"自从重盛兄长过世 父亲便在福原隐居不出","from":240.85,"location":2,"to":245.46},{"content":"看来是伤得很深","from":246.34,"location":2,"to":248.92},{"content":"但是 我们不能一直消沉下去","from":253.42,"location":2,"to":256.44},{"content":"即便兄长不在了","from":256.64,"location":2,"to":257.84},{"content":"我们也必须继承平家","from":257.92,"locati